Project Name: QuickHire

Tech Stack:
Frontend: Next.js 16, React 19, TailwindCSS
Backend: Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, Mongoose
Authentication: JWT + HTTP-only Cookies
File Uploads: Multer (CV upload)

Project Description:
এই project-এ দুটি main user role আছে:
Admin – Jobs & Categories management, view applications.
User – Browse jobs, filter by category, view job details, apply jobs with CV.

Project এর মূল feature:
Admin login/logout, CRUD for Jobs & Categories
Jobs listing with category filter
Job application with file upload (CV)
Secure authentication with JWT cookies